      • enableHeartbeat

        public abstract void enableHeartbeat()
        Enables the heartbeat mechanism for this TSProvider's TSAPI session, via the TSProvider's Tsapi object. If this method is called before the Tsapi object has been constructed, then a flag is set to enable the heartbeat mechanism when construction of the Tsapi object is complete.

      • disableHeartbeat

        public abstract void disableHeartbeat()
        Disables the heartbeat mechanism for this TSProvider's TSAPI session, via the TSProvider's Tsapi object. If this method is called before the Tsapi object has been constructed, then this request is ignored.
